# Configuration Design

#### Configuration Design <a id="configuration-design"></a>

Different components usage and indication cased will be introduced.  
**Screen**  
Various screens can be included in configuration interface, you will enter main menu if you enter the devices details. Other screens can be jumped through screen switching components. Each screen can be configured separately.

**Dragging and Adding Components**  
Components can be dragged to screen through left components column, and you can move it to correspondent position then loose the mouse. Ctrl+ direction key can be used for position small adjusting

![Alt text](data:image/gif;base64,)

**Properties Modification by Double Click**  
Double click components, set components basic properties such as components position and size,numeric components variables, and different status labels of switch components.

![Alt text](data:image/gif;base64,)

**Tool Bar**  
Common function buttons can be provided such as “save”,”delete”,”copy”,”paste”,”cancel”,”cut” etc, components alignment ways and layers can be set.
